snippet: U.S. military officials have grounded all F-35s while continuing to investigate a runway fire involving one of the fighter jets at Eglin Air Force Base in Florida....

headline.print_headline: Military Grounds All F-35 Jets During Fire Probe
headline.main: Military Grounds All F-35 Jets During Fire Probe

lead_paragraph: U.S. military officials have grounded all F-35s while continuing to investigate a runway fire involving one of the fighter jets at Eglin Air Force Base in Florida.
